outline:
1. to give, provide, ascribe, come
    1. (Qal)
      1. to give
      2. to set, place
      3. to provide (with reflexive)
      4. to ascribe (glory)
      5. to grant, permit, come now
kjv_def: ascribe, bring, come on, give, go, set, take.
strongs_def: to give (whether literal or figurative); generally, to put; imperatively (reflexive) come
